				<p>There are a number of different <abbr title="Search engine optimisation">SEO</abbr> keyword tools and they often provide different results &ndash; it&rsquo;s good to use more than one to understand the right keywords to use:</p>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="http://www.semrush.com">SEMrush</a></li>
					<li><a href="http://www.google.co.uk/trends/">Google Trends</a></li>
